For the checklist, use a tap-through design: each item shows the description with three large buttons (✅ Pass, ❌ Fail, ➖ N/A). The currently selected result is highlighted. Tapping again on the same result deselects it (back to NotChecked).

Per-item notes: a small "Add note" link that expands a textarea below the item.

```razor
@page "/new-inspection"
@page "/new-inspection/{SiteId}"
@using SiteInspector.Client.Services
